{"tid":2343026,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜商場狂播聖誕洗腦歌吸金  DONKI yuu聽到精神崩潰  心理學家指是耳蟲效應有方法自救","createTime":"2020-12-27T14:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:08:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8dbe0d1affd5b7cbc999e04c4fea52f27154cd3","tid":2343026,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"平安夜商場狂播聖誕洗腦歌吸金 <br />\nDONKI yuu聽到精神崩潰 <br />\n心理學家指是耳蟲效應有方法自救<br />\n#健康蘋台─果籽 <br />\n香港 Apple Daily<br />\n─原刊日期：20201223<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rIahychP3Is\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrIahychP3Is&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=17182004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rIahychP3Is</a><br />\n<br />\n果籽<br />\n612K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n踏入12月，不少商場仍然在疫情下佈置聖誕裝飾，大播聖誕歌來增添節日氣氛，務求向消費者不斷洗腦。有臨床心理學家指出，其實此舉是一種耳蟲效應。<br />\n<br />\n除了聖誕歌，驚安の殿堂DONKI和牛奶公司獎賞計劃YUU的主題曲也是耳蟲效應的很好例子。臨床心理學家鄒凱詩（Daisy）解釋，如果腦袋中不停播同一首歌停不了，其實已出現了耳蟲效應的反應。Daisy認為，這些容易洗腦的歌，都有共同特徵，包括節奏較快、歌詞淺白簡單、有節奏感、中間有停頓及起伏位。而漫不經心、沒在用腦、想要分心、太過疲累、壓力大的情況更容易被歌洗腦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/2...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F2...&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=4abc2815\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F2...&h=3eee9b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/2...</a>"},{"pid":"36d3f46ba13ec132db629ef35c19577748140668","tid":2343026,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"Yuu..."},{"pid":"11fed3d26bae1627c72d6c42bd4978b4adafb992","tid":2343026,"uid":47500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"一聽到聖誕歌同入donki個腦就自動唱黑色聖誕同班popo感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63efa3deaf0245864d2e7e5483ef90fa33